				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13627470/scp-5738#post-4765933</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 03 Sep 2020 12:02:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ShadowSpirit90</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6753095</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This scip started out sounding awesome, like something I would love to have happen to me. I mean, an extended period of time where I have some peace and solitude and can pretty much do whatever I want? Who wouldn't want that? And then, things went dark when you showed the science and sheer and utter loneliness of what this would bring. It makes me hate Flemming, even though you never really even learn much about him. Seriously, this is fantastic, and I am so glad I was able to read it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
